---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = "About Us";
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description="Learn about the Balanced Feminine Path mission and the woman behind the brand.">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="page-label">About</span>
      <h1>Our Story</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        A sanctuary for women seeking alignment, healing, and authentic living.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>The Beginning</h2>
        <p>
          Balanced Feminine Path was born from a personal journey—a path of self-discovery, 
          healing, and ultimately, transformation. After years of navigating the complexities 
          of modern womanhood, dealing with burnout, and searching for authentic connection, 
          the need for a space like this became clear.
        </p>
        <p>
          This isn't just another wellness blog. It's a carefully curated space where science 
          meets soul, where ancient wisdom meets modern understanding, and where every woman 
          can find resources that honor her unique journey.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          We believe in the power of the feminine—not as a limitation, but as a profound 
          strength. The qualities often seen as "soft" or "intuitive" are actually powerful 
          tools for navigating life: deep feeling, creative wisdom, nurturing presence, and 
          the ability to hold space for complexity.
        </p>
        <p>
          True balance isn't about doing everything perfectly or achieving some idealized 
          state. It's about alignment—living in accordance with your values, honoring your 
          needs, and creating a life that feels authentic and nourishing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">♡</span>
          <h3>Compassion</h3>
          <p>Approaching ourselves and others with kindness and understanding.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">☽</span>
          <h3>Intention</h3>
          <p>Living with purpose and making conscious choices aligned with our values.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">✧</span>
          <h3>Authenticity</h3>
          <p>Honoring our true selves without pretense or people-pleasing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <span class="value-icon">❋</span>
          <h3>Holistic Wellness</h3>
          <p>Recognizing the connection between mind, body, and spirit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <ul class="offerings-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Thoughtful Articles</strong> — Deep dives into topics that matter: hormonal 
            health, mental wellness, spiritual growth, and intentional living.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Practical Resources</strong> — Guides, worksheets, and tools you can 
            actually use in your daily life.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Community Support</strong> — A judgment-free space where women can 
            connect, share, and grow together.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Holistic Approaches</strong> — Integrating conventional wisdom with 
            natural, evidence-based practices.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block cta-block">
        <h2>Join the Journey</h2>
        <p>
          Whether you're just beginning to explore these topics or you've been on this 
          path for years, there's a place for you here. We're so glad you're here.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/blog" class="btn">Explore the Blog</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-bg) 0%, var(--color-bg-alt) 100%);
    padding: 5rem var(--spacing) 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content {
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .content-block {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .content-block p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 3rem auto;
  }

  .value-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .offerings-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .offerings-list li {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-bg-alt);
  }

  .offerings-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .offerings-list strong {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .cta-block {
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    .content-block h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>